<subpara id="RM000000WU2047X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000000WU2047X_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00003HW00000">
<ptxt>CHECK CAMSHAFT TIMING OIL CONTROL VALVE ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A099015E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Connect the intelligent tester to the DLC3.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Start and warm up the engine.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Select VVT from the Active Test menu.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>With the engine idling, check the engine speed when the oil control valve is operated by the intelligent tester.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>VVT system is OFF (Oil control valve is OFF)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Normal engine speed</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>VVT system is ON (Oil control valve is ON)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Rough idle or engine stalled</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the result is not as specified, replace the oil control valve assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
